{"data":[{"date":"03:21 26/06","title":"HLV Nga: \u201c\u0110\u00e3 bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hlv-nga-da-biet-truoc-chung-toi-van-bat-luc-truoc-uruguay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Cherchesov ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay 3-0 Nga. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, Nga v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n 3 b\u00e0n thua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nga th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNga \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng A c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Uruguay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Saudi Arabia 5-1 v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp 3-1 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng A.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean Nga tr\u00ean BXH FIFA song h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Uruguay x\u1ebfp 14 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 x\u1ee9 b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng mong ch\u1edd \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 m\u01a1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nga \u0110\u00e3 bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Nga \u0110\u00e3 bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/HLV-Nga-Da-biet-truoc,-chung-toi-van-bat-luc-truoc-Uruguay-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nga th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay, Nga \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. H\u1ecd thua chung cu\u1ed9c 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 b\u1edfi c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Luis Suarez, Edinson Cavani b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh 1 pha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Denis Cheryshev. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf m\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Igor Smolnikov c\u1ee7a Nga nh\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd th\u00eam \u00ea ch\u1ec1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Cherchesov ch\u1ec9 ra nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Cherchesov ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay 3-0 Nga. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 54 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, Nga v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Cherchesov\" title=\"HLV Cherchesov\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/hlv-nga-da-biet-truoc-chung-toi-van-bat-luc-truoc-uruguay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Cherchesov ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay 3-0 Nga \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp h\u00f4m qua, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh 20 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp c\u00e1c b\u00e0i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t. V\u00e0 h\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. M\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh ri\u00eang. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o n\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n</em>&rdquo;, Cherchesov n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i kh\u00e1ch quan. \u00c1p l\u1ef1c m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1edbn</em>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Nga tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. HLV Cherchesov n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;<em>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chu \u0111\u00e1o nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3</em>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Uruguay 3-0 Nga tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-tabarez-phat-bieu-sau-tran-uruguay-30-nga-421-189561.html\">HLV Uruguay n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n v\u00f9i d\u1eadp ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-uruguay-30-nga-421-189559.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay 3-0 Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-uruguay-vs-nga-461-189550.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Uruguay 3-0 Nga (B\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-uruguay-vs-nga-463-189532.html\">Uruguay 3-0 Nga (KT): H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t g\u1ea5u Nga, La Celeste to\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"579","checkdouble":"189563"},{"date":"05:25 26/06","title":"H\u1ecfng pen, Ronaldo v\u1eabn gi\u00fap World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/diem-nhan-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-noi-that-vong-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong hi\u1ec7p 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pen trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nN\u01b0\u1edbc Nga &ldquo;ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea3o&rdquo; v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 11m c\u1ee7a Ronaldo trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-463-189553.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 gi\u1eefa Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span>, k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 ghi nh\u1eadn s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng penalty k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c &ndash; 19 l\u1ea7n t\u00ednh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh, k\u1ef3 World Cup 2014 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Brazil ch\u1ec9 ghi nh\u1eadn 13 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n to\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i. Trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u qu\u1ea3 11m nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay (18 l\u1ea7n) v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1990, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c san b\u1eb1ng \u1edf c\u00e1c n\u0103m 1998 v\u00e0 2002.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, x\u1ee9 s\u1edf b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1ecdi k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, d\u00f9 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a \u0111i qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00e3 ra t\u0103ng, m\u00e0 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a VAR. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 video g\u1ed3m t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng ekip b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh), kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ecf qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pen \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ed5i\" title=\"Ronaldo h\u1ecfng pen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/diem-nhan-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-noi-that-vong-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>World Cup 2018&nbsp;l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pen \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVAR v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 sau. To\u00e0n b\u1ed9 clip \u1edf m\u1ecdi g\u00f3c quay s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem x\u00e9t k\u1ef9 trong ph\u00f2ng video b\u1edfi 4 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i chu\u1ea9n FIFA, trong m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng. V\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng tr\u00f9ng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 VAR, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o, sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f9y t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1y ra ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i qua b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ecdi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7 CR7 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u00fat h\u1ecfng. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pen \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ed5i, v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat nh\u01b0 Ronaldo v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, n\u1ebfu c\u0103n c\u1ee9 theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng penalty cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga s\u1ebd c\u00f2n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i, g\u1ea5p ba con s\u1ed1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hazard-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-sieu-ky-luc-sau-64-nam-421-189367.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00ec ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-421-189557.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-421-189557.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nChuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Iran 1-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)<br>\r\n</span>\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Iran \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25/6.<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"578","checkdouble":"189564"},{"date":"06:51 26/06","title":"4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau m\u00e0n \u201ch\u00fat ch\u1ebft\u201d c\u1ee7a TBN tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/diem-nhan-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Iran m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 su\u00fdt n\u1eefa b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n. Sau tr\u1eadn, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Iran \u2013 HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i vung tay v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t Morteza Pouraliganji c\u1ee7a Iran. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec v\u1ec1 pha \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u00e0y, khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng VAR \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sau kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00ec theo d\u00f5i b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh, v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 trao cho Ronaldo m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng. Trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iran \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n l\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i. B\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra khi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, HLV Carlos Queiroz c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng: &ldquo;Theo lu\u1eadt, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n gi\u1eadt ch\u1ecf v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0103n th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 Messi hay Ronaldo. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra khi \u0111\u00f3. C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ai ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m. Khi c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ebfn VAR, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft ai l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Carlos Queiroz doi phat the do Ronaldo\" title=\"HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/red.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;VAR l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng kh\u00e1 m\u01a1 h\u1ed3, v\u00e0 th\u00fa th\u1ef1c t\u00f4i v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u00e0o hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, b\u0103ng ghi h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u l\u00fd do g\u00ec tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1edbt l\u1edd. Khi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec m\u1ed9t pha th\u00fac c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra hay kh\u00f4ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf - nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Uruguay, trong khi Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eabn b\u00ecnh y\u00ean v\u00f4 s\u1ef1 khi ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Iran 1-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Iran \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25/6.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc-421-189564.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/diem-nhan-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-noi-that-vong-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc-421-189564.html\">H\u1ecfng pen, Ronaldo v\u1eabn gi\u00fap World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nTrong hi\u1ec7p 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pen trong...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"577","checkdouble":"189565"},{"date":"04:06 26/06","title":"Suarez \"n\u1ed5\" t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng sau khi \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/suarez-no-tung-bung-sau-khi-da-bai-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Luis Suarez mong mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00f9ng Uruguay sau khi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay.</h2><h2>Suarez l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Suarez \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap Uruguay gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Uruguay \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n trong 3 k\u1ef3 World Cup li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Suarez ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga h\u00f4m qua. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u cho <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-uruguay-vs-nga-463-189532.htmlabc\" target=\"_blank\">m\u00e0n v\u00f9i d\u1eadp ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Uruguay.</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Suarez n\u1ed5 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng sau khi Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Suarez n\u1ed5 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng sau khi Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/suarez-no-tung-bung-sau-khi-da-bai-nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Suarez n\u1ed5 to sau khi gi\u00fap Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nga</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Suarez t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o Uruguay l\u1eadp th\u00eam nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cM\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111i t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a World Cup. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sinh ra l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1. \u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u1edbi v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau khi th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay. T\u00f4i m\u1eebng v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. B\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Uruguay th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf World Cup v\u00e0 n\u1eafm gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n, ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>L\u00fd do Uruguay ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uruguay b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nga v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i sau khi \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm ch\u1eafc t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Oscar Tabarez \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 Suarez cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cNh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng h\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u00edt b\u1ecb \u00e1p l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n v\u00e0 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</em><strong><em>Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs Nga:</em></strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-uruguay-vs-nga-461-189550.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Uruguay 3-0 Nga (B\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Nga:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-tabarez-phat-bieu-sau-tran-uruguay-30-nga-421-189561.html\">HLV Uruguay n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n v\u00f9i d\u1eadp ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bang-xep-hang-bxh-bang-a-world-cup-2018-421-189547.html\">B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng chung cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"576","checkdouble":"189566"},{"date":"04:42 26/06","title":"Salah nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/salah-nhan-loi-sau-chien-dich-world-cup-tham-hoa-cua-ai-cap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 xin l\u1ed7i c\u00e1c C\u0110V sau khi Ai C\u1eadp b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o.</h2><h2>Ai C\u1eadp b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Salah b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span> khi m\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp g\u1eb7p Uruguay. Anh ghi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u1edbt ch\u00fat \u00edt danh d\u1ef1 cho Ai C\u1eadp \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah xin l\u1ed7i C\u0110V Ai C\u1eadp sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Salah xin l\u1ed7i C\u0110V Ai C\u1eadp sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/salah-nhan-loi-sau-chien-dich-world-cup-tham-hoa-cua-ai-cap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Salah xin l\u1ed7i C\u0110V\u00a0Ai C\u1eadp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Salah \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng m\u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1edbm cho Ai C\u1eadp v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Saudi Arabia. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng v\u00e0 r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTruy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nga \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra c\u00e3i c\u1ecd sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac. V\u00e0 Salah l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n l\u00ean xe bus c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd tha th\u1ee9 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n xin l\u1ed7i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi t\u1eadn n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi h\u1ecd, c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2022\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Salah kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110TQG</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Hector Cuper \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n d\u1eadp tan tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Salah s\u1ebd t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp sau tr\u1eadn thua Saudi Arabia. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn t\u1ea1i sao c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ecbp bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u1ea1i sao Salah kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 b\u00e1c s\u0129 nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00fd do c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 \u01b0? T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u00fd c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 g\u00ec. Theo nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Salah s\u1ebd t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 tin \u0111\u1ed3n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt b\u1edfi v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-saudi-arabia-vs-ai-cap-461-189549.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Saudi Arabia 2-1 Ai C\u1eadp (B\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bang-xep-hang-bxh-bang-a-world-cup-2018-421-189547.html\">B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng chung cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-saudi-arabia-vs-ai-cap-421-189538.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"575","checkdouble":"189567"},{"date":"06:07 26/06","title":"B\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c, HLV Iran l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00f2i th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/queiroz.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Iran m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 su\u00fdt n\u1eefa b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n. Sau tr\u1eadn, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Iran \u2013 HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i vung tay v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t Morteza Pouraliganji c\u1ee7a Iran. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec v\u1ec1 pha \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u00e0y, khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng VAR \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sau kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00ec theo d\u00f5i b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh, v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 trao cho Ronaldo m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng. Trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iran \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n l\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i. B\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra khi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, HLV Carlos Queiroz c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng: &ldquo;Theo lu\u1eadt, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n gi\u1eadt ch\u1ecf v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0103n th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 Messi hay Ronaldo. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra khi \u0111\u00f3. C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ai ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m. Khi c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ebfn VAR, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft ai l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Carlos Queiroz doi phat the do Ronaldo\" title=\"HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/red.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;VAR l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng kh\u00e1 m\u01a1 h\u1ed3, v\u00e0 th\u00fa th\u1ef1c t\u00f4i v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u00e0o hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, b\u0103ng ghi h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u l\u00fd do g\u00ec tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1edbt l\u1edd. Khi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec m\u1ed9t pha th\u00fac c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra hay kh\u00f4ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf - nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Uruguay, trong khi Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eabn b\u00ecnh y\u00ean v\u00f4 s\u1ef1 khi ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Iran 1-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Iran \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25/6.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc-421-189564.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/diem-nhan-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-noi-that-vong-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc-421-189564.html\">H\u1ecfng pen, Ronaldo v\u1eabn gi\u00fap World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nTrong hi\u1ec7p 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pen trong...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"574","checkdouble":"189569"},{"date":"06:23 26/06","title":"HLV Santos n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hlv-santos-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-may-man-cua-bo-dao-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Fernando Santos chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Iran.\r\n</h2><h2>Santos h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng knock-out<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ricardo Quaresma gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong hi\u1ec7p 1, trong khi Ansarifard \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Iran \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Fernando Santos \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gi\u00e1p m\u1eb7t Uruguay \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 pha th\u00fac c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a CR7, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t may anh kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/bat-luc-hlv-iran-len-tieng-doi-the-do-cho-ronaldo-421-189569.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Carlos Queiroz c\u1ee7a Iran \u0111\u00f2i th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Ronaldo</span>. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u00f4ng Santos cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a VAR. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 VAR \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Fernando Santos chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Iran\" title=\"Fernando Santos\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/hlv-santos-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-may-man-cua-bo-dao-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Fernando Santos chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Iran</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Fernando Santos ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c. &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u1ef9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, sau \u0111\u00f3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Uruguay hay \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1c nhau, Nga \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Uruguay c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, nh\u01b0ng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Uruguay. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Fernando Santos chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Iran.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bat-luc-hlv-iran-len-tieng-doi-the-do-cho-ronaldo-421-189569.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/queiroz.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bat-luc-hlv-iran-len-tieng-doi-the-do-cho-ronaldo-421-189569.html\">B\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c, HLV Iran l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00f2i th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Iran m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 su\u00fdt n\u1eefa b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n. Sau tr\u1eadn, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Iran &ndash; HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Iran 1-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Iran \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25/6.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"573","checkdouble":"189570"},{"date":"06:04 26/06","title":"HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ea7y lo \u00e2u sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a nh\u1ecdc Ma R\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hlv-hierro-phat-bieu-sau-tran-tbn-22-ma-roc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn TBN 2-2 Ma R\u1ed1c. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i cho \u00f4ng nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i lo l\u1edbn.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>TBN su\u00fdt thua Ma R\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng B. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, La Roja ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t Ma R\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i v\u00e0 tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i m\u1ecdi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea3o ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ma R\u1ed1c t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3 quan chia tay World Cup 2018 trong khi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ea7y mong manh. Ngay ph\u00fat 14, s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u0103n \u00fd gi\u1eefa Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 Sergio Ramos \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Khalid Boutaib b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t De Gea v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn TBN 2-2 Ma R\u1ed1c v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 lo \u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn TBN 2-2 Ma R\u1ed1c v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 lo \u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/HLV-Hierro-phat-bieu-sau-tran-TBN-2-2-Ma-Roc-voi-su-lo-au-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ma R\u1ed1c khi\u1ebfn cho TBN\u00a0ph\u1ea3i \"h\u00fat ch\u1ebft\"</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n5 ph\u00fat sau, Iniesta chu\u1ed9c l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u1ecdn c\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 Isco qu\u00e2n b\u00ecnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1. Nh\u01b0ng khi c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u1ea1i b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 sai l\u1ea7m. H\u1ecd b\u1ecf l\u1ecfng Youssef En-Nesyri b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u00fap Ma R\u1ed1c d\u1eabn 2-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i t\u1edbi ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Iago Aspas c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1edbi gi\u00fap TBN c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 may m\u1eafn cho La Roja l\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd, khi m\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ecb Iran c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n 1-1, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng B.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi c\u00e1c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga (nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng A) \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 trong khi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha g\u1eb7p Uruguay (nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng A).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Hierro kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Telecinco sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Fernando Hierro \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110TQG ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup cho hay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. \u201c<em>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng</em>\u201d, Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn TBN 2-2 Ma R\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hierro\" title=\"HLV Hierro\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/hlv-hierro-phat-bieu-sau-tran-tbn-22-ma-roc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn TBN 2-2 Ma R\u1ed1c v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 ph\u00ea b\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 x\u1ea5u x\u00ed trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i xem l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. M\u1ecdi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ec1u nguy hi\u1ec3m. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra nguy hi\u1ec3m cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn TBN 2-2 Ma R\u1ed1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc-461-189562.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2-2 Mar\u1ed1c (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc-421-189558.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Ma r\u1ed1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-tay-ban-nha-vs-maroc-463-189554.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2-2 Mar\u1ed1c (KT): Nh\u1edd VAR, La Roja th\u00f3t tim v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"572","checkdouble":"189572"},{"date":"06:53 26/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u TBN 2-2 Ma R\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-tbn-22-ma-roc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u TBN 2-2 Ma R\u1ed1c l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng B VCK World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n- B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Khalid Boutaib cho Ma R\u1ed1c t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ee9 29 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- B\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ma R\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1998 khi Salaheddine Bassir l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Scotland trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Sergio Ramos \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 16 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Xavi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u TBN 2-2 Ma R\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u TBN 2-2 Ma R\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-tbn-22-ma-roc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Iniesta v\u00e0 Isco \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u TBN 2-2 Ma R\u1ed1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 23 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi thua Italia t\u1ea1i Euro 2016.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ma R\u1ed1c ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau 10 tr\u1eadn World Cup v\u1eeba qua (thua 7, h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1982, sau khi th\u1eafng 8 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u TBN 2-2 Ma R\u1ed1c, Isco \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tham gia v\u00e0o 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 15 tr\u1eadn qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y (10 b\u00e0n, 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Iago Aspas \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 10 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha (6 b\u00e0n, 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2006 khi to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau TBN 2-2 Maroc\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u TBN 2-2 Mar\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Thong-so-TBN.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u TBN 2-2 Mar\u1ed1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn TBN 2-2 Ma R\u1ed1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-hierro-phat-bieu-sau-tran-tbn-22-ma-roc-421-189572.html\">HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ea7y lo \u00e2u sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a nh\u1ecdc Ma R\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc-461-189562.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2-2 Mar\u1ed1c (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-tay-ban-nha-vs-maroc-463-189554.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2-2 Mar\u1ed1c (KT): Nh\u1edd VAR, La Roja th\u00f3t tim v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"571","checkdouble":"189573"},{"date":"06:53 26/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u0110N 1-1 Iran","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-sau-tran-dau-bdn-11-iran.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u0110N 1-1 Iran l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng B VCK World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n- B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 4 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed (sau n\u0103m 1966, 2006 v\u00e0 2010).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Iran \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup trong c\u1ea3 5 VCK h\u1ecd tham d\u1ef1 (1978, 1998, 2006, 2014 v\u00e0 2018).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Iran t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi \u1edf th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd (94:06 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c, 92:48 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u0110N 1-1 Iran h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u0110N 1-1 Iran h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-sau-tran-dau-bdn-11-iran.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo \u0111i b\u00f3ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u0110N 1-1 Iran</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Sau tr\u1eadn B\u0110N 1-1 Iran, Ricardo Quaresma (34 tu\u1ed5i 272 ng\u00e0y) tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb Yahya Golmohammadi (35 tu\u1ed5i 84 ng\u00e0y) cho Iran v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2006.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Iran l\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c gia ch\u00e2u \u00c1 th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng sau H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u0103m 2006.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- 2 trong 3 qu\u1ea3 penalty m\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran (th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u0103m 2006 nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn cho B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 50% (v\u00e0o 2, tr\u01b0\u1ee3t 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Iran kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng trong c\u1ea3 8 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u t\u1ea1i World Cup (thua 6, h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua mu\u1ed9n nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ea1i World Cup (92 ph\u00fat 48 gi\u00e2y).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng thua tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i World Cup sau khi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc (th\u1eafng 13, h\u00f2a 3).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Iran 1-1 Bo Dao Nha\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 1-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Thong-so-Iran-vs-BDN.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 1-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u0110N 1-1 Iran tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-santos-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-may-man-cua-bo-dao-nha-421-189570.html\">HLV Santos n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bat-luc-hlv-iran-len-tieng-doi-the-do-cho-ronaldo-421-189569.html\">B\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c, HLV Iran l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00f2i th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc-421-189564.html\">H\u1ecfng pen, Ronaldo v\u1eabn gi\u00fap World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc-461-189562.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2-2 Mar\u1ed1c (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"570","checkdouble":"189574"},{"date":"16:31 25/06","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Ronaldo thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u201cch\u00fa d\u00ea\u201d Messi c\u00f3 bu\u1ed3n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/goc-nhin-chung-kien-ronaldo-thi-dau-chu-de-messi-co-buon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 c\u1eb7p k\u1ef3 ph\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong 10 n\u0103m qua, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa 2 si\u00eau nh\u00e2n n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Ronaldo v\u1eabn t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n, c\u00e1c C\u0110V l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Lionel Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nT\u1eeb &ldquo;ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u d\u00ea&rdquo; c\u1ee7a CR7<br>\r\n<em>&nbsp;</em></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;Quaresma n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nu\u00f4i ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u n\u1ebfu ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ng\u00e0y mai&rdquo;</em> &ndash; <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ly-do-hai-huoc-khien-ronaldo-quyet-dinh-nuoi-rau-de-421-189143.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e2u</span>, 1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf World Cup. \u0110\u00f3 v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a CR7, khi anh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 lu\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111i\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e0, ch\u1ea3i chu\u1ed1t, Ronaldo l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 g\u00e3 &ldquo;th\u1ea7y tu&rdquo; \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a \u1edf cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng. Khi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U, m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 Ronaldo &ndash; h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Evra l\u1ea1i ph\u00e1t ho\u1ea3ng khi th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e0n em ch\u1ec9 u\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ecdc v\u00e0 \u0103n th\u1ecbt tr\u1eafng, tuy\u1ec7t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ch\u1ea5t k\u00edch th\u00edch n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n c\u1ee7a CR7. Anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 h\u00ecnh x\u0103m n\u00e0o. Th\u1eadm cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33 &ndash; c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong \u0111\u1eddi Ronaldo&hellip; nu\u00f4i r\u00e2u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u c\u1ee7a CR7 \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Ronaldo thi \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fa d\u00ea Messi c\u00f3 bu\u1ed3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Goc-nhin-Chung-kien-Ronaldo-thi-dau,-chu-de-Messi-co-buon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo v\u00e0 &quot;ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u d\u00ea&quot; m\u1edbi nu\u00f4i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ec9nh cao trong su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m li\u1ec1n, v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u1eabn nh\u01b0 ch\u00e0ng trai 23 tu\u1ed5i, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i kh\u1ed5 luy\u1ec7n h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00ednh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh. Sau tu\u1ed5i 30, Ronaldo ti\u1ebfn h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm, \u01b0a th\u00edch v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng cho d\u00f9 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t anh ch\u00e0ng m\u00e0u m\u00e8, \u01b0a bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n t\u1ea1i \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0o Euro 2004, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y Ronaldo thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 g\u00e1nh c\u1ea3 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u00ean vai. Anh \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 b\u1eaft c\u1ea3 \u0110T ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i B\u0110N nh\u01b0 bao ki\u1ebfm, t\u1ea1o m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 thanh g\u01b0\u01a1m Ronaldo xu\u1ea5t v\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-01h00-ngay-266-kho-can-cr7-421-189482.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0110T Iran</span>. T\u1ea1i sao n\u00f3i &ldquo;g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i&rdquo;, b\u1edfi v\u00ec b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ronaldo t\u1ea1i World Cup, ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Iran (n\u0103m 2006 t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c). V\u00e0 trong k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \u01b0a th\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. B\u1edfi \u00edt ra, Ronaldo c\u0169ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u c\u1ee7a CR7 \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup: Ronaldo 4 - Messi 0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Ronaldo 4 - Messi 0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>V\u00e0 &ldquo;ch\u00fa d\u00ea&rdquo; t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p Lionel Messi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 mang ti\u1ebfng &ldquo;c\u00f4ng t\u1eed&rdquo;, &ldquo;con nh\u00e0 l\u00e0nh&rdquo;, Messi c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng k\u00e9m ai \u1edf kho\u1ea3n x\u0103m h\u00ecnh hay&hellip; nu\u00f4i r\u00e2u, nhu\u1ed9m t\u00f3c. Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m di\u1ec5n ra VCK World Cup, anh c\u00f2n cho ra l\u00f2 b\u1ed9 \u1ea3nh ch\u1ee5p c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t con d\u00ea (goat), v\u1edbi \u00fd ngh\u0129a<strong> &ldquo;Greastest of All Time&rdquo; </strong>(hay nh\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i). T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Messi qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, n\u00ean anh c\u00f3 t\u1ef1 tin m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng sao.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/cuu-sao-barca-che-messi-khong-bang-ronaldo-421-189430.html\" target=\"_blank\">Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Ronaldo</span> &ndash; \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia. Messi, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f9ng Argentina, khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn cho r\u1eb1ng anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. V\u00e0 c\u1ee9 sau m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, anh l\u1ea1i thay \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n h\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta&hellip; th\u1ea5t t\u00ecnh.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u c\u1ee7a CR7 \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/mess.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lionel Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, Messi l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh g\u1ed3ng g\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, hay th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn Argentina ph\u00e1t huy s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh. Jorge Sampaoli, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Argentina hi\u1ec7n nay, n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh theo&hellip; s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u1ee7a El Pulga.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Icardi v\u00e0 Dybala r\u1ea5t hay, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf nh\u00e0, ng\u01b0\u1eddi &ldquo;m\u00f2n \u0111\u00edt&rdquo; d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00ec Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch. Higuain, d\u00f9 lu\u00f4n v\u00f4 duy\u00ean trong nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, v\u1eabn g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n, ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec Messi th\u00edch. Hay nh\u01b0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina-465-189202.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sampaoli th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch&hellip; to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Argentina</span>, v\u00ec &ldquo;d\u00e1m&rdquo; che m\u1edd v\u1ea7ng h\u00e0o quang c\u1ee7a Messi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, Albiceleste kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 10. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Messi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 &ldquo;g\u00e1nh&rdquo; \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia theo \u00fd, nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Ronaldo \u0111ang l\u00e0m. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh CR7 l\u00e0 &ldquo;thanh ki\u1ebfm&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n quanh &ldquo;v\u1ecf bao&rdquo; B\u0110N, Messi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc khi\u00ean \u0111\u1ee1 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Argentina &ndash; \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t m\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t b\u1edfi Croatia 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n cho&hellip; Nigeria h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Iceland \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2. V\u00e0 tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00e0n lan b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh Messi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Nigeria, 2 tay gi\u01a1 cao v\u00e0 \u0103n m\u1eebng nh\u01b0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u c\u1ee7a CR7 \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Messi h\u1eb3n r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi Nigeria th\u1eafng Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/messsi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi h\u1eb3n r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi Nigeria th\u1eafng Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Leo \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n. Trong bu\u1ed5i sinh nh\u1eadt m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y (24/6) c\u1ee7a anh, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u vui v\u1ebb v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi b\u1ecf n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n thua tr\u1eadn sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean. Messi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t keo h\u00e0n g\u1eafn v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2y ra b\u1edfi Sampaoli.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/thua-tham-croatia-argentina-phai-lam-gi-de-vuot-qua-vong-bang-421-189208.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Argentina bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Nigeria</span>. V\u00e0 th\u1eadt may m\u1eafn, khi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 mi\u1ebfng m\u1ed3i quen thu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i World Cup n\u00e0o Nigeria kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p Argentina, th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3&hellip; kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i World Cup. Trong 6 l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi 5 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p Albiceleste, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 thua 4 l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1 10 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. B\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng, n\u1ebfu Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, anh v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 &ldquo;ch\u00fa d\u00ea&rdquo; t\u1ef1 phong, v\u00e0 cay \u0111\u1eafng nh\u00ecn Ronaldo &ldquo;v\u1ec3nh r\u00e2u&rdquo; h\u1ebft tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y sang tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tuoi-31-cua-lionel-messi-mot-dam-me-mot-dai-kho-mot-si-389-189418.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/tuoi-31-cua-lionel-messi-mot-dam-me-mot-dai-kho-mot-si.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tuoi-31-cua-lionel-messi-mot-dam-me-mot-dai-kho-mot-si-389-189418.html\">Tu\u1ed5i 31 c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi: M\u1ed9t \u0111am m\u00ea, m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1i kh\u1edd, m\u1ed9t Si</span><br>\r\n4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Messi \u0111\u00f3n sinh nh\u1eadt tu\u1ed5i 27 b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac trong tr\u1eadn Argentina th\u1eafng Nigeria 3-2 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. 4 n\u0103m sau &ndash;...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ha-nhuc-argentina-sao-croatia-con-khinh-bi-khong-them-doi-ao-voi-messi-421-189368.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/ha-nhuc-argentina-sao-croatia-con-khinh-bi-khong-them-doi-ao-voi-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ha-nhuc-argentina-sao-croatia-con-khinh-bi-khong-them-doi-ao-voi-messi-421-189368.html\">H\u1ea1 nh\u1ee5c Argentina, sao Croatia c\u00f2n &ldquo;khinh b\u1ec9&rdquo; kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m \u0111\u1ed5i \u00e1o v\u1edbi Messi</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 trong tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Argentina &ndash; Rebic coi th\u01b0\u1eddng Messi v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/20180621T195318Z_273911651_RC1220A4E800_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGCRO.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eafng Argentina 3-0 h\u00f4m 21/6, Croatia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"569","checkdouble":"189520"},{"date":"16:35 25/06","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/u19-viet-nam-ton-that-nhan-su-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh b\u1ecb g\u00e3y tay tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh  tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh  tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/tien-anh-0007.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh B c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may b\u1ecb g\u00e3y tay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande B, Ti\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e3 \u1edf t\u01b0 th\u1ebf b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ed1ng tay ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111au. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ch\u1ee5p phim cho th\u1ea5y Ti\u1ebfn Anh b\u1ecb g\u00e3y x\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00e1nh tay v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Ti\u1ebfn Anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, khi m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi tranh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (25/6) th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Ri\u00eang Ti\u1ebfn Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1n b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a VFF \u1edf l\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c th\u00eam \u00edt ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ca ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o VFF sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb, \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Ti\u1ebfn Anh c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadp trung \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c. V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eeba g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i, Ti\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Indonesia trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"568","checkdouble":"189523"},{"date":"16:42 25/06","title":"\"Th\u00e1nh h\u1ed5\" d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ra sao v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/thanh-ho-du-doan-ra-sao-ve-ket-qua-tran-uruguay-vs-nga.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 John Stones ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf Everton trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh vs B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh hai v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n knock-out.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/quy-tac-xep-hang-bang-dau-world-cup-2018-tai-sao-anh-vs-bi-co-the-phan-dinh-nhat-nhi-bang-the-phat-421-189499.html\">Quy t\u1eafc x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh vs B\u1ec9 Stones th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Lukaku ng\u00e0y t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Anh vs B\u1ec9 Stones th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Lukaku ng\u00e0y t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/nguoi-anh-thach-thuc-ngoi-no-lukaku-trong-tran-chien-voi-bi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Stones h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Lukaku \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 John Stones, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m c\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a Harry Kane khi ghi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong m\u00e0n h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Anh 6-1 Panama, \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Romelu Lukaku, ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn \u0111ang th\u0103ng hoa phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi 4 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Stones v\u00e0 Lukaku t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean nhau trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Everton tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn hai n\u1eeda th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3. Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i cho m\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i v\u00e0 Rom t\u1eebng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai ng\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Everton. Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1eady n\u00ean Man Utd m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ch\u1ecbu chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh \u1ea5y. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec t\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng mong ng\u00f3ng m\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi Rom.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eaft c\u00e1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia-421-189373.html\" target=\"_blank\">B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia</span> v\u00e0 t\u1edbi gi\u1edd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n ngh\u00eanh chi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. N\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n th\u00ec qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e2 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Roberto Martinez.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bi-tunisia-lukaku-nguoi-di-tim-cau-tra-loi-cho-moi-cau-hoi-421-189389.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/san-bang-thanh-tich-cua-ronaldo-lukaku-noi-gi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bi-tunisia-lukaku-nguoi-di-tim-cau-tra-loi-cho-moi-cau-hoi-421-189389.html\">B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia: Lukaku \u2013 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i t\u00ecm c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho m\u1ecdi c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi</span><br>\r\n\u1ede s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 World Cup, m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o mang danh \u201cch\u00e2n g\u1ed7\u201d hay \u201ckh\u00f4ng n\u00e3o\u201d nh\u01b0 Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e0n anh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"567","checkdouble":"189524"},{"date":"17:18 25/06","title":"Carragher: \"\u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n b\u00f3p n\u00e1t B\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/carragher-dt-can-bop-nat-bi-o-tran-dau-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Jamie Carragher, \u0110T Anh n\u00ean b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i.</h2><h2>Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 tranh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m qua sau khi \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Panama v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 6-1 t\u1ea1i Nizhny Novgorod. \u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick, qua \u0111\u00f3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng G, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-thach-thuc-ngoi-no-lukaku-trong-tran-chien-voi-bi-421-189527.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi B\u1ec9</span>. \u0110\u1ed9i n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. V\u00e0 Carragher cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Tam S\u01b0 g\u1eedi chi\u1ebfn th\u01b0 t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Carragher hy v\u1ecdng Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Carragher hy v\u1ecdng Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/carragher-dt-can-bop-nat-bi-o-tran-dau-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Carragher hy v\u1ecdng Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n cho Anh, tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Brazil ho\u1eb7c \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Senegal c\u00f3 Sadio Mane v\u00e0 Ismaila Sarr trong khi Colombia c\u0169ng \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ch\u1eafc c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a qu\u00ean nh\u1eefng l\u1ea1c quan m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Iceland c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 thay v\u00ec ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out. Gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra ni\u1ec1m tin trong l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00edch nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0110T Anh\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Anh kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf th\u1ebf c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Carragher, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o th\u1ebf c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Southgate c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cKh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh \u1edf Champions League, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng cao h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ea1c quan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u0103m nay, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ti\u1ebfp theo m\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Southgate c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-thach-thuc-ngoi-no-lukaku-trong-tran-chien-voi-bi-421-189527.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 Lukaku trong tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-len-day-cot-tinh-than-truoc-dai-chien-voi-dt-anh-421-189486.html\">Courtois l\u00ean d\u00e2y c\u00f3t tinh th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"566","checkdouble":"189525"},{"date":"16:53 25/06","title":"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0103n may, kh\u00f3 \u0111i s\u00e2u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/hlv-le-thuy-hai-nhan-dinh-dt-nhat-ban-an-may-kho-di-sau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng may v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ph\u00f9 tang kh\u00f3 \u0111i s\u00e2u.</h2><h2>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eafng may</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 1. Sang t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai, \u2018c\u00e1c Samurai xanh\u2019 ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Senegal ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Le Thuy Hai tu tin co the lam tot vi tri GDKT o doi tuyen Viet Nam\" title=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed G\u0110KT \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/10/22/hlv-hai-lo-toi-tu-tin-co-the-lam-tot-gdkt-o-doi-tuyen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i xa t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i t\u00e2m s\u1ef1 tr\u00ean Vietnamnet: \u201cTh\u1ef1c ra b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec gh\u00ea g\u1edbm c\u1ea3.\u00a0\u1ede\u00a0tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, Colombia m\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1edbm v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i trong hi\u1ec7p 2 n\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.Tr\u1eadn h\u00f4m qua Nh\u1eadt c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n g\u00ec\u00a0Senegal, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed may m\u1eafn g\u1ee1\u00a0h\u00f2a v\u00e0 c\u1ed1\u00a0gi\u1eef\u00a0k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3\u00a0\u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3\u00a0c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e2n t\u00edch k\u1ef9 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i \u2018l\u01a1\u2019 cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: \u201c\u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd\u00a0Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea7n ch\u01a1i ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nhanh, nh\u1ecf, ban b\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3\u00a0ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi th\u1ec3\u00a0h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 th\u1ec3\u00a0l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hai tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua h\u1ecd\u00a0kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3\u00a0hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec r\u00f5 n\u00e9t. T\u00f4i xin nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong th\u00ec c\u0169ng l\u00e0 do may m\u1eafn b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7\u00a0t\u1ef1\u00a0thua, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec c\u0169ng th\u1ebf\u00a0th\u00f4i, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e2u\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb c\u1ef1u G\u0110KT Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cB\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00ec v\u1ee9t, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 World Cup. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9\u00a0khen Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ea3\u00a0c\u1ea3m, chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t th\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c ra \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o t\u1edbi World Cup ch\u1eb3ng v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0\u00a0Panama h\u1ecd\u00a0thua \u0111\u1eadm nh\u01b0\u00a0th\u1ebf\u00a0nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3\u00a0c\u00f3 b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1. Ba Lan c\u0169ng v\u1eady, h\u1ecd\u00a0b\u1ecb\u00a0lo\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd\u00a0bu\u00f4ng xu\u00f4i c\u1ea3. H\u00e3y c\u1ee9\u00a0xem tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0\u00a0n\u00e0o v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\u201d, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n l\u00e3o l\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam hy v\u1ecdng \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp song \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Akira Nishino b\u1edfi t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup</span> c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 chung kh\u00e1t khao chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuc-dien-bang-h-truoc-luot-tran-cuoi-cho-doi-nhung-bat-ngo-421-189462.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/cuc-dien-bang-h-truoc-luot-tran-cuoi-cho-doi-nhung-bat-ngo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuc-dien-bang-h-truoc-luot-tran-cuoi-cho-doi-nhung-bat-ngo-421-189462.html\">C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng H tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i: \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp?</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Colombia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. V\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-nhat-ban-sang-cua-di-tiep-dung-coi-thuong-nhung-chang-lun-466-189471.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/dt-nhat-ban-sang-cua-di-tiep-dung-coi-thuong-nhung-chang-lun.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-nhat-ban-sang-cua-di-tiep-dung-coi-thuong-nhung-chang-lun-466-189471.html\">\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: \u0110\u1eebng coi th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1eefng ch\u00e0ng l\u00f9n</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi HLV Akira Nishino ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u1edbi con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hoa-qua-cam-cua-dt-nhat-ban-truoc-senegal-421-189460.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/Du-am-Nhat-Ban-2-2-Senegal-Tinh-than-Samurai-va-niem-hy-vong-chau-A-hinh-anh-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hoa-qua-cam-cua-dt-nhat-ban-truoc-senegal-421-189460.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Senegal</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 hai l\u1ea7n san h\u00f2a c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"565","checkdouble":"189526"}]}